            <td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 20px; color: #222222;"><p style="margin: 0 0 15px; padding: 0;"><strong>Core Programme Roles  available to deliver NCS with The Challenge.</strong><br /><br /><strong>Programme Manager</strong> x 2 (Birmingham office)<br />&#13;
            £30,000 pro rata<br />&#13;
            Fixed Term - 1st May - 30th  September or 28th November<br /><br /><strong>Assistant Programme  Manager</strong> (London, Birmingham and  Manchester)<br />&#13;
            £21,000 (London) £18,375 (outside  London) pro rata <br />&#13;
            Fixed term - 1st May - 14th  October or 28th November <br /><br /><em>We have  approximately 40 roles available nationally.</em><br /><br />&#13;
            Please go to our website for more info <a href="http://the-challenge.org/year-round-roles" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #ec008c;">the-challenge.org/year-round-roles</a></p></td>&#13;
            <td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>&#13;
            </tr><tr><td width="600" height="15" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"></td>&#13;
            </tr><tr><td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>&#13;
