            <td width="550">&#13;
            	<table width="550" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td width="375" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 20px; color: #222222;"><p style="margin: 0 0 15px; padding: 0;"><span style="color: #00aeef; font-size: 20px; line-height: 25px;">New Year...New You?</span></p>&#13;
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 15px; padding: 0;"><strong>The Challenge has 40 places on this year’s  famous British 10K run, 13th July 2014.</strong></p>&#13;
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 15px; padding: 0;">We are giving priority to all summer staff so sign up NOW before they go on sale within our networks. To register your  place it costs £20, with a minimum sponsorship target of £100.</p>&#13;
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 15px; padding: 0;">If you are interested please contact Ruth on  <a href="mailto:ruth.galea@the-challenge.org" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #ec008c;">ruth.galea@the-challenge.org</a> or 07838391194 to register your place. This will  include the added bonus of regular health and fitness emails to spur you on</p>&#13;
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 15px; padding: 0;"><strong>Go on... you know you want to!</strong></p></td>&#13;
                <td width="175" align="left" valign="top"><img src="http://ncsthechallenge.org/Staffing/newsletter-030314/alumni-run-graphic-280214.jpg" alt="Sign up today" width="175" height="140" border="0" /></td>&#13;
                </tr></table></td>&#13;
            <td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>&#13;
            </tr><tr><td width="600" height="15" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"></td>&#13;
